title: PROFESSIONAL FIGHTERS LEAGUE PARTNERS WITH SPORTSICON TO CREATE THE PFL METAVERSE EXPERIENCE
summary: NEW YORK, Nov. 10, 2022 /PRNewswire/ -- The Professional Fighters League, the fastest growing and most innovative sports league, today announced a partnership with SportsIcon, the NFT platform for athletes and collectors, to create the PFL MMA Metaverse.
